  "description": "Get a fun and clear weather report sent to your phone automatically! 📰\n\nThis little bot wakes up, checks the weather for you, and builds a super simple summary of your day.\n\nWhat it does:\n\n🌡️ Grabs the current temperature and what it actually feels like.\n\n📉 Figures out the high and low for the whole day.\n\n📅 Gives you a 5-day forecast so you can plan your week.\n\n✈️ Sends it all to you in a clean Telegram message!\n\nSetup is easy:\nJust plug in your info for Telegram, add your location, and you're good to go! ✨",
